A1. Use LSTM, Bi-LSTM networks for speech recognition. Use STFT / STCT, MFCC & LPC coefficients.
A2. Speak the sentence “Bhanumathi weds Rajat” (भानुमति वेड्स रजि || భానుమతి వెడ్స్ రజత్). 
Construct speech for the word “Bharat” (భారత్ || भारत || ಭರತ್ || பாரத்) by combining segmented phonemes taken from “Bhanumathi weds Rajat” speech recording. 
Listen to this word speech generated and note down the issues associated with this approach of speech synthesis. The string written Indian scripts may have some error. 
Please validate before using.
